{"tid":446891,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]作為半個IT狗都搞唔掂","createTime":"2017-10-24T17:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T15:57:18.000Z","uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4197af88ea8bc7ed4702a0e7ae5c67be9a0e3fd9","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"我用唔到64bit 既browser 上網(firefox同chrome)<br />\n以下係firefox既error圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=23ecf93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一開始就係用緊firefox上網睇video,"},{"pid":"fc35b4fc75654d2d610835eba0f73144b4d68f2c","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用唔到64bit 既browser 上網(firefox同chrome)<br />\n以下係firefox既error圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=23ecf93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一開始就係用緊firefox上網睇video,</blockquote><br />\n之後我記得個網要用到adobe flash既  <br />\n<br />\n咁一load就彈 'plugin container for firefox已經停止運作' 成個firefox會彈左重開<br />\n<br />\n咁我就去更新flash啦 都係唔得 咁就再去update firefox<br />\n<br />\n點之就越搞越死 update左之後就連開個page上網都用唔到 出上面個error<br />\n<br />\n咁我就開始debug <br />\n<br />\nAVG + bitdefender full scan左<br />\n<br />\ncmd sfc /scannow + chkdsk c:/r 都做過<br />\n<br />\n只係用到32bit 既 browser"},{"pid":"0e0822039a70173630d2691bccc4180b361a1bf7","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"所以想問下各位IT高手應該點搞好<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩可能性<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28cbe867ac7c5b05a7ab99a8c43931390e468ad","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用唔到64bit 既browser 上網(firefox同chrome)<br />\n以下係firefox既error圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F011451_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=23ecf93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一開始就係用緊firefox上網睇video,</blockquote><br />\n之後我記得個網要用到adobe flash既  <br />\n<br />\n咁一load就彈 'plugin container for firefox已經停止運作' 成個firefox會彈左重開<br />\n<br />\n咁我就去更新flash啦 都係唔得 咁就再去update firefox<br />\n<br />\n點之就越搞越死 update左之後就連開個page上網都用唔到 出上面個error<br />\n<br />\n咁我就開始debug <br />\n<br />\nAVG + bitdefender full scan左<br />\n<br />\ncmd sfc /scannow + chkdsk c:/r 都做過<br />\n<br />\n只係用到32bit 既 browser</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 因為太急打小<br />\n<br />\n仲有已經試左delete 哂所有add-ons 同flash 再restart firefox都唔得<br />\n<br />\n當我入windows safe mode 再開 64bit browser就用到"},{"pid":"2a66f0af4b634f968c774173712d300dcb274522","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80058a8accde1823b0e7ae5203732e197707189f","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"當我重新註冊dll果時<br />\n<br />\ncmd &gt; for %1 in (%windir%\\system32\\*.dll) do regsvr32.exe /s %1<br />\n<br />\n又會出一個error<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=0bff81f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3daf192340e31bfed7df5ff1682d161ebed178d9","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81944c78dfd481c00b3fdb5f7526a85e9ede9fc5","tid":446891,"uid":59933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"試下用x86"},{"pid":"7c382d72288e5d25e18748a5a0f0790da7d76cc9","tid":446891,"uid":61347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當我重新註冊dll果時<br />\n<br />\ncmd &gt; for %1 in (%windir%\\system32\\*.dll) do regsvr32.exe /s %1<br />\n<br />\n又會出一個error<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=0bff81f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺係 C++ 可轉發元件 library file corrupt左，上m$ down 過裝啦"},{"pid":"5a3166273d84967a85649b0a59f73c80a8c65bdc","tid":446891,"uid":133217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:26:36.000Z","msg":"行一次「sfc /scannow」睇下?"},{"pid":"c037f66e9de8b81fc46ad9416aaf4c7627c03fb1","tid":446891,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:51:15.000Z","msg":"linux"},{"pid":"5308c157d0547eca873beee0018814c007cf62f7","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行一次「sfc /scannow」睇下?</blockquote><br />\n行過 完成到 冇發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7596524cafaae49ad37b68727336b5424260177b","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下用x86</blockquote><br />\n姐係用32bit？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc026c1754f5ac286f44e6431f76a16b85b4e8b","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當我重新註冊dll果時<br />\n<br />\ncmd &gt; for %1 in (%windir%\\system32\\*.dll) do regsvr32.exe /s %1<br />\n<br />\n又會出一個error<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=0bff81f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺係 C++ 可轉發元件 library file corrupt左，上m$ down 過裝啦</blockquote><br />\n我一陣試 唔該哂巴打"},{"pid":"1cd74529e46564b6c146c82b5766198f6761e163","tid":446891,"uid":59933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下用x86</blockquote><br />\n姐係用32bit？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個windows係32 定64bit先？"},{"pid":"663a31c77092e82d59c9f8b1f372a16ec3ede8b3","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下用x86</blockquote><br />\n姐係用32bit？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個windows係32 定64bit先？</blockquote><br />\n64bit"},{"pid":"06df6fdba42f533954a12a83690a0dc89ad54a3e","tid":446891,"uid":60522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"其實32bit同64bit既browser差係邊到?"},{"pid":"b95ebb8f892bfebb259f357f526ff3b75e9a4d74","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當我重新註冊dll果時<br />\n<br />\ncmd &gt; for %1 in (%windir%\\system32\\*.dll) do regsvr32.exe /s %1<br />\n<br />\n又會出一個error<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=0bff81f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺係 C++ 可轉發元件 library file corrupt左，上m$ down 過裝啦</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打 我岩先裝左Visual Studio 2017 <br />\n<br />\n可以用得番64bit firefox上網 但當我開新tab個時又會出同一個unknown software exception 0x80000003 error 不過都照上到<br />\n<br />\n64bit chrome就出<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/130558_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F130558_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG&h=160c71f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到重新註冊dll果時都出同一個error<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打!! 起碼用得番firefox先"},{"pid":"a70943343ad0e148d18efb35fd56d690e7d7d82b","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實32bit同64bit既browser差係邊到?</blockquote><br />\n簡單來講係快啲<br />\n<br />\n同埋有啲software 64bit先compatible"},{"pid":"449ddaaed0b5563248f3dc245ddb02e6684e705f","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當我重新註冊dll果時<br />\n<br />\ncmd &gt; for %1 in (%windir%\\system32\\*.dll) do regsvr32.exe /s %1<br />\n<br />\n又會出一個error<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F014558_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=0bff81f6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺係 C++ 可轉發元件 library file corrupt左，上m$ down 過裝啦</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打 我岩先裝左Visual Studio 2017 <br />\n<br />\n可以用得番64bit firefox上網 但當我開新tab個時又會出同一個unknown software exception 0x80000003 error 不過都照上到<br />\n<br />\n64bit chrome就出<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/130558_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F130558_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG&h=160c71f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到重新註冊dll果時都出同一個error<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打!! 起碼用得番firefox先</blockquote><br />\n原來都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我refresh firefox之後又變番一開就彈error<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c455a814e2a5e8b2b44aae2fe5a56a76838728","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5985f7932e8ee16880fafea37c24cf78cf2a01d6","tid":446891,"uid":133217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"有時間嘅話我建議你重裝OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34bc19c1d07b4884453cfdf83718b9147d420bd","tid":446891,"uid":60996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時間嘅話我建議你重裝OS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa